<section class="w-section">
  <div class="w-inner">
    <p class="w-eyebrow reveal"><span class="w-glyph" aria-hidden="true">●</span> Weather</p>
    <h2 class="w-h2 reveal" data-stagger="2">Every signal that drives a weather market.<br />Cleaned, reconciled, and&nbsp;settlement-grade.</h2>

    <div class="w-body reveal" data-stagger="3">
      <p>Kalshi runs daily high-temp markets on twenty US cities. Polymarket extends the shape internationally. Both settle on official station data, published in formats designed for meteorologists, not&nbsp;traders.</p>
      <p>We pulled the whole stack into one place. Source-priority dedup. T-group precision so live matches archive. Settlement windows in Local Standard Time. Climate withheld until the NWS publication threshold&nbsp;passes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="w-source-line reveal" data-stagger="4">
      <span class="label">Ingest:</span>
      <span>AWC</span><span class="sep">/</span>
      <span>IEM</span><span class="sep">/</span>
      <span>NCEI GHCNh</span><span class="sep">/</span>
      <span>NWS CLI</span><span class="sep">/</span>
      <span>IEM MOS</span><span class="sep">/</span>
      <span>Open-Meteo</span><span class="sep">/</span>
      <span>GOES-16</span><span class="sep">/</span>
      <span>GOES-19</span>
    </div>

    <div class="w-stat-row reveal">
      <div class="w-stat">
        <span class="w-stat-num">60+</span>
        <span class="w-stat-label">cities<br />Kalshi + Polymarket</span>
      </div>
      <div class="w-stat">
        <span class="w-stat-num">77</span>
        <span class="w-stat-label">years of history<br />since 1948</span>
      </div>
      <div class="w-stat">
        <span class="w-stat-num">5</span>
        <span class="w-stat-label">forecast models<br />NBM · GFS · HRRR · ECMWF</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
